The Pink Quartz beads accented with silver colored beads and bail, with a double sided "Japanese girl" charm. The adult bracelet measures approximately 6 1/2 inches (16 cms), while the child sized bracelet measures approximately 5 inches (12.5 cms).

description:

I have used this with all my stretch bracelets and have had no trouble to date, including with my three year old wearing hers (on and off a few dozen times a day!).
